strawn.evariant.rainsorter.engine

Class RainsorterEngine

  • java.lang.Object
    • strawn.evariant.rainsorter.engine.RainsorterEngine

  • public class RainsorterEngine
extends Object
    This class is the main workhorse of rainsorter. All needed data sets meet here, and are connected in a meaningful way This class computes the population wetness.
